snippet.title: Highwater Consoles Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Highwater is a post-apocalyptic adventure strategy experience like none other. Join Nikos and crew as they fight to survive a flooded, war-torn Earth in hopes of a better life on Mars. Featuring gorgeous visuals, a unique blend of gameplay, and an incredible soundtrack, Highwater is drowning in both style and substance.
